author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Praktiker Real Estate Polska buys 477,203 shares of Regnon
text:
Oct 15 Regnon SA :
* Said on Wednesday that Praktiker Real Estate Polska Sp. z o.o. acquired 477,203 shares of Regnon for 1 zloty per share
* Praktiker Real Estate Polska is affiliated with the company's supervisory board member, Cezary Liskiewicz,
